#CircuitBreakerSG D-29
Tonight, we're having Batang Mackerel 2-way; Sweet & Sour or dip in Tangerine Sauce. What say you?

The other 2 dishes are Broccoli & Acar.

Enjoy your #dinner too!

The two-way batang is so tempting!! But I also want to dip mackerel in tangerine sauce.. I am so greedy 🤣
Luv ur every dish especially the batang😋😋
I had Batang for dinner today too!
Oooo both sound so good! I can't pick 😂
I say fantastic as always!! If only I can eat this for lunch now!! 🤗😋😍
Yummy! The sweet n sour fish makes you want to bite into it!😍

Thank you for pledging to #StayHomeWithAscott. #CapitaLandHopeFoundation will be making a donation of US$10 to Save The Children and we look forward to more of your #StayHomeWithAscott posts. Stay home, stay safe and cook away!
Everything looks delicious! Must have been a very nice meal 😊
